    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Italian stuffed quilting technique worked in smaller and narrower areas, creating almost the appearance of corded quilting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
